The '''Rago Run''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] anchored by the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Rago/Legends|Rago]]. It was the closest main hyperroute to pass near the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]]. It was connected to the [[Utegetu Nebula/Legends|Utegetu Nebula]] by many minor routes, including the [[Murgo Choke]].

